WEBVTT

00:01:01.210 --> 00:01:03.300
One fine spring day...

00:01:03.340 --> 00:01:06.040
a disciple looked at some branches
blowing in the wind.

00:01:06.080 --> 00:01:07.550
He asked his master...

00:01:08.680 --> 00:01:14.350
"Master, are the branches moving
or is it the wind?"

00:01:15.320 --> 00:01:18.580
Not even glancing to where
his pupil was pointing...

00:01:18.630 --> 00:01:19.850
the master smiled and said...

00:01:21.030 --> 00:01:26.960
"That which moves is neither
the branches nor the wind..."

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:28.560
"It's your heart and mind."

00:01:45.150 --> 00:01:48.180
Sunwoo, you should
go downstairs for a moment.

00:01:48.220 --> 00:01:49.180
Why?

00:01:49.220 --> 00:01:50.450
There's some trouble.

00:01:54.790 --> 00:01:55.920
Okay, I'll handle it.

00:03:48.570 --> 00:03:51.700
I'm sorry, but
business hours are over.

00:03:51.740 --> 00:03:56.000
Please get up and leave
before I count to three. One.

00:04:01.850 --> 00:04:03.110
Two.

00:04:06.920 --> 00:04:07.920
Three!

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:12.090
Sit down, stupid!

00:04:17.530 --> 00:04:18.590
Min-gi, lock the door.

00:04:37.780 --> 00:04:38.870
You son of a bitch!

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:55.360
See you tomorrow.

00:04:55.400 --> 00:04:56.440
- See you tomorrow.
- Okay.

00:05:09.050 --> 00:05:13.240
Yes, boss. I'll transfer
the money in the morning.

00:05:14.820 --> 00:05:16.460
All right, we'll close
for the night, sir.

00:06:06.830 --> 00:06:08.630
So, did you take care
of yesterday's business?

00:06:08.680 --> 00:06:09.680
Yes, sir.

00:06:10.470 --> 00:06:13.530
Good. You always seem
to get things done.

00:06:16.580 --> 00:06:20.470
It looks like Chairman Baek's son
is the one making trouble.

00:06:20.510 --> 00:06:23.870
Yes, it didn't seem like
Chairman Baek did it himself.

00:06:23.920 --> 00:06:26.910
Chairman Baek's son used
to be a loan shark...

00:06:26.950 --> 00:06:29.250
I heard he's interested
in this business.

00:06:29.290 --> 00:06:30.350
Abalone, sir.

00:06:30.990 --> 00:06:34.620
There's talk that he started
dealings with Southeast Asia.

00:06:34.660 --> 00:06:35.660
Why?

00:06:37.030 --> 00:06:43.730
He's pushing businesses to hire
Filipina girls instead of Russians.

00:06:43.770 --> 00:06:48.230
Assholes. Like father, like son.

00:06:49.940 --> 00:06:50.940
It's me...

00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:52.680
Moon Suk.

00:06:55.080 --> 00:06:57.910
I shouldn't have brought my car...

00:06:57.950 --> 00:06:59.580
I hope I'm not interrupting?

00:07:00.990 --> 00:07:01.990
Oh, it's okay.

00:07:02.650 --> 00:07:04.050
What's that? Abalone?

00:07:04.090 --> 00:07:05.550
Get another for me.

00:07:05.590 --> 00:07:06.590
Yes, sir.

00:07:10.360 --> 00:07:12.520
Hey, sorry about yesterday.

00:07:13.200 --> 00:07:15.890
I can't believe that happened.
I just stepped out for a second.

00:07:15.930 --> 00:07:17.490
You must have been busy
enough upstairs.

00:07:22.710 --> 00:07:25.300
Those guys yesterday
were just local boys.

00:07:25.340 --> 00:07:26.740
Nothing to worry about, sir.

00:07:27.410 --> 00:07:30.540
- What do you think you're doing?
- Sir?

00:07:30.580 --> 00:07:32.340
Is this how you do business?

00:07:33.580 --> 00:07:35.810
- It was just...
- Get out now.

00:07:35.850 --> 00:07:37.290
Get out and wait for me!

00:08:02.340 --> 00:08:04.200
Be smart.

00:08:04.250 --> 00:08:06.310
Things are going good for you now.

00:08:06.950 --> 00:08:08.940
But the world is not easy.

00:08:08.980 --> 00:08:14.110
You can do 100 things right, but
one mistake can destroy everything.

00:08:15.490 --> 00:08:16.980
Okay, I'll keep that in mind.

00:08:18.960 --> 00:08:21.990
I'll try to sort things out
with Chairman Baek.

00:08:22.030 --> 00:08:26.560
Anyhow, the real reason
I asked you here...

00:08:26.600 --> 00:08:30.600
I have to go to Shanghai
tomorrow afternoon on business...

00:08:30.640 --> 00:08:32.940
I have a favor to ask
before I leave.

00:08:36.180 --> 00:08:37.270
The thing is...

00:08:43.120 --> 00:08:44.440
Pour me a drink.

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:45.480
Oh, yes, sir. Sorry.

00:08:54.230 --> 00:08:55.990
The truth is,

00:08:59.970 --> 00:09:02.160
I have a young girlfriend.

00:09:03.070 --> 00:09:05.800
Someone I really care about.

00:09:05.840 --> 00:09:08.930
She's not like you and me.
She's a special kind of person.

00:09:13.680 --> 00:09:15.610
What, am I boring you?

00:09:17.780 --> 00:09:18.980
Uh... Congratulations, sir.

00:09:19.020 --> 00:09:21.940
Never mind "Congratulations."

00:09:21.990 --> 00:09:25.850
The problem is, I think
She's seeing a new guy.

00:09:25.890 --> 00:09:27.690
Some young guy is hanging around her.

00:09:28.830 --> 00:09:32.390
It's driving me crazy,
and I couldn't tell anyone else.

00:09:33.030 --> 00:09:36.020
You know, you're the only one
I can really talk to about this.

00:09:36.800 --> 00:09:40.240
No one else knows how much
this worries me.

00:09:41.270 --> 00:09:45.370
So, I'd like you to watch Heesoo
for just three days.

00:09:46.710 --> 00:09:47.870
Watch her?

00:09:48.480 --> 00:09:51.570
Watch over her.
Take care of her.

00:09:51.620 --> 00:09:53.280
See if she's really seeing someone.

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:55.280
Maybe the bastard's just bothering her.

00:09:55.320 --> 00:09:58.150
See whether she's given him
her body and soul and all.

00:09:59.390 --> 00:10:05.990
You know young people,
a hand could brush a shoulder...

00:10:06.030 --> 00:10:08.590
then they hold hands, then kiss,
and then... you know...

00:10:08.630 --> 00:10:10.500
These things happen.

00:10:14.270 --> 00:10:18.930
But I can't stand thinking
about her like that.

00:10:19.910 --> 00:10:20.970
Stupid, isn't it?

00:10:21.010 --> 00:10:22.100
No, sir.

00:10:22.650 --> 00:10:24.200
Stupid.

00:10:24.250 --> 00:10:27.710
So... I want you to find out
who she's meeting.

00:10:27.750 --> 00:10:30.140
And what she does when they meet.

00:10:30.190 --> 00:10:31.680
Just for 3 days.

00:10:32.450 --> 00:10:36.390
This is Heesoo's address
and phone number.

00:10:37.830 --> 00:10:44.660
I hope she's not seeing him,
but if she is...

00:10:44.700 --> 00:10:48.690
If they look like they're involved...

00:10:48.740 --> 00:10:50.640
Call me right away.
Or finish them off yourself.

00:10:51.210 --> 00:10:52.260
Excuse me?

00:10:53.810 --> 00:10:57.170
You know I can't stand
being lied to, right?

00:10:57.210 --> 00:11:00.140
Love isn't love if you're
being lied to.

00:11:00.180 --> 00:11:02.410
You can contact me here
in Shanghai.

00:11:02.450 --> 00:11:03.540
Directly.

00:11:08.090 --> 00:11:09.090
Have a good night.

00:11:10.420 --> 00:11:13.050
Do you have a girlfriend?

00:11:13.660 --> 00:11:15.050
No, sir.

00:11:15.090 --> 00:11:16.920
Have you ever been in love?

00:11:16.960 --> 00:11:19.920
No, you haven't.

00:11:19.970 --> 00:11:23.190
That's why I'm entrusting you
with this job.

00:11:23.240 --> 00:11:25.200
That's why I like you.

00:11:28.170 --> 00:11:29.540
Okay, let's go.

00:11:31.010 --> 00:11:32.010
Goodbye, sir!

00:13:11.110 --> 00:13:14.430
President Kang told me
to give this to you personally.

00:13:14.480 --> 00:13:15.480
I'm sorry?

00:13:16.380 --> 00:13:18.570
President Kang told me
to give this to you personally.

00:13:20.750 --> 00:13:21.750
What's that?

00:13:59.890 --> 00:14:02.750
Wow, it's so funny-looking.

00:14:05.590 --> 00:14:06.920
It's so like Mr. Kang.

00:14:07.990 --> 00:14:08.990
It's cute.

00:14:10.200 --> 00:14:11.250
Don't you think so?

00:14:44.800 --> 00:14:47.420
Hello, not yet.

00:14:48.970 --> 00:14:51.230
Already? Hold on a second...

00:14:59.580 --> 00:15:02.270
President Kang also said
I should drive you today.

00:15:02.310 --> 00:15:05.080
Oh, I don't need a ride.
You can go, it's fine.

00:15:06.050 --> 00:15:08.610
- He said I should take you myself.
- I'll let him know about it.

00:15:10.620 --> 00:15:13.150
Well, then, I'll see you later.

00:15:16.690 --> 00:15:20.450
If you need anything,
please contact me here.

00:15:20.500 --> 00:15:22.190
It's okay, I don't need it.

00:15:24.100 --> 00:15:25.570
Oh, give it to me anyway.

00:15:28.570 --> 00:15:29.830
Goodbye.

00:15:49.790 --> 00:15:51.880
Heesoo, Heesoo.

00:17:55.780 --> 00:17:58.800
They sure like to get around...
Maybe it's because they're still young?

00:18:01.780 --> 00:18:03.050
Why isn't she getting out?

00:18:50.660 --> 00:18:52.430
Hey, Moon Suk. Everything okay?

00:18:54.070 --> 00:18:55.070
What?

00:18:58.200 --> 00:19:01.060
President Baek, that asshole...

00:19:01.110 --> 00:19:02.970
He keeps calling and bothering me.

00:19:03.010 --> 00:19:04.970
Asking how could we do this to him.

00:19:05.010 --> 00:19:07.940
He says he lost face
because of you.

00:19:07.980 --> 00:19:10.810
He wants to meet you.

00:19:10.850 --> 00:19:17.480
I said no, his guys were to blame.

00:19:18.060 --> 00:19:21.350
But he insists on meeting you.

00:19:21.390 --> 00:19:23.920
He's calling me
every 10 minutes.

00:19:23.960 --> 00:19:25.850
I think you should...

00:19:25.900 --> 00:19:29.020
What the...
Who's bugging me now?

00:19:30.130 --> 00:19:34.500
See? He's calling again.
I'm sick of getting it.

00:19:34.540 --> 00:19:36.100
You take care of it now.

00:19:52.360 --> 00:19:54.190
Hello, this is Kim Sunwoo.

00:20:01.160 --> 00:20:04.620
Well, if you have something to say,
Come here and tell me yourself.

00:20:04.670 --> 00:20:06.160
I'm hanging up.

00:20:09.070 --> 00:20:10.470
I took care of it.

00:20:11.270 --> 00:20:17.140
Hello, hello.
He... hello? Hello?

00:20:17.180 --> 00:20:20.140
Fucker, hung up on me.

00:20:20.180 --> 00:20:23.010
What a rude bastard. Hello?

00:20:23.050 --> 00:20:24.180
Should I?

00:20:24.220 --> 00:20:25.480
Leave it!

00:20:35.730 --> 00:20:41.500
Laughing? You think that's funny?
Funny huh?

00:20:43.840 --> 00:20:48.100
You go around smiling like an idiot...
That's why you get your ass kicked.

00:20:48.140 --> 00:20:50.800
Damn you bastard, look at me.

00:20:50.840 --> 00:20:53.140
Look at me, damn it.

00:20:55.450 --> 00:20:56.570
Funny?

00:20:57.950 --> 00:20:59.980
I'm sorry, sir.

00:21:01.750 --> 00:21:02.750
Do you think it's funny?

00:21:02.790 --> 00:21:05.220
Funny, funny, funny?

00:21:05.260 --> 00:21:07.250
Funny?

00:21:10.930 --> 00:21:12.190
Shit!

00:21:19.370 --> 00:21:21.900
What hell were you thinking?
You're making it even worse!

00:21:27.310 --> 00:21:29.210
Hey, this is your job.

00:21:29.250 --> 00:21:31.340
I took care of it
because you weren't there.

00:21:31.380 --> 00:21:34.180
This kind of thing is your job.
You should've taken care of it.

00:21:34.220 --> 00:21:36.450
They just want to do business
with us...

00:21:36.490 --> 00:21:40.720
and beat us to the punch
before starting to deal.

00:21:40.760 --> 00:21:42.230
Don't you get it?

00:21:42.860 --> 00:21:45.420
What are you lecturing me now?

00:22:15.090 --> 00:22:17.020
Hey, get the phone over here.

00:22:17.060 --> 00:22:18.150
Yes sir.

00:22:21.060 --> 00:22:22.190
Here, sir.

00:22:29.100 --> 00:22:32.000
What an idiot.

00:22:32.040 --> 00:22:33.630
What? Is this voice dial?

00:22:36.510 --> 00:22:39.710
Don't you think we need
to press the numbers?

00:22:40.380 --> 00:22:41.620
Should I dial it with my mouth?

00:22:46.490 --> 00:22:48.720
Stupid motherfuckers.

00:22:51.130 --> 00:22:53.950
Call Moosung from Samseongyo.

00:22:54.000 --> 00:22:55.000
Yes, sir.

00:23:38.900 --> 00:23:42.770
You didn't answer your mobile,
so I'm leaving this message.

00:23:42.810 --> 00:23:46.800
If you have some time, I need
your help for a little while.

00:23:46.850 --> 00:23:51.340
Just until 3 in the afternoon.
After that, it's fine.

00:23:51.380 --> 00:23:52.940
If you get this message...

00:23:52.980 --> 00:23:54.410
Yes, it's me. It's Sunwoo.

00:23:54.450 --> 00:23:59.520
Ah, yes. At what time?
And right now it's...

00:24:00.530 --> 00:24:02.590
I'll be there in an hour
at the latest.

00:24:02.630 --> 00:24:04.060
I'm on my way.

00:24:31.890 --> 00:24:36.480
Mr. Kang said you're a scary guy.

00:24:37.660 --> 00:24:39.030
Excuse me?

00:24:39.630 --> 00:24:40.720
He did?

00:24:42.200 --> 00:24:43.500
Yes...

00:24:51.410 --> 00:24:53.000
You're an enforcer, aren't you?

00:24:57.710 --> 00:24:59.770
I gave you my card the other day.

00:24:59.820 --> 00:25:01.310
I work at a hotel.

00:25:07.390 --> 00:25:09.020
So you're an enforcer for the hotel?

00:25:09.060 --> 00:25:10.350
I'm not that kind of person.

00:25:18.500 --> 00:25:20.060
You're so boring to talk to.

00:25:31.350 --> 00:25:32.840
Can I ask you something?

00:25:32.880 --> 00:25:34.110
Sure.

00:25:37.280 --> 00:25:38.560
How did you first meet Mr. Kang?

00:25:38.600 --> 00:25:41.090
- Wait a minute.
- Okay.

00:25:42.990 --> 00:25:44.580
How much is the red lamp?

00:25:44.620 --> 00:25:46.450
$280

00:25:46.490 --> 00:25:48.950
$280?

00:25:49.000 --> 00:25:51.860
- Okay, bye.
- Bye.

00:25:54.030 --> 00:25:55.030
Let's go.

00:26:00.470 --> 00:26:02.500
What were you saying?

00:26:02.540 --> 00:26:05.510
You asked why I am seeing Mr. Kang?

00:26:07.010 --> 00:26:08.270
Yes.

00:26:09.150 --> 00:26:10.940
Why do you want to know?

00:26:12.780 --> 00:26:16.350
It's just... you don't have
to answer.

00:26:22.790 --> 00:26:24.820
- Hello.
- Hello.

00:26:28.330 --> 00:26:30.060
I'll take that now.

00:26:37.340 --> 00:26:38.530
I'm sorry.

00:26:38.580 --> 00:26:39.870
For what?

00:26:40.410 --> 00:26:42.140
Asking you those questions.

00:26:43.380 --> 00:26:44.780
It's okay.

00:26:46.050 --> 00:26:49.610
Thanks for your time today.
I didn't want to eat by myself.

00:26:49.650 --> 00:26:52.650
If you'd like to take a look,
you can enter through that door.

00:26:52.690 --> 00:26:54.180
How will you return home?

00:26:54.220 --> 00:26:58.420
It's easy to catch a cab here.

00:27:12.070 --> 00:27:13.400
You guys ready?

00:27:13.440 --> 00:27:15.140
- Yeah, ready.
- Okay.

00:27:17.050 --> 00:27:18.480
Let's go.

00:28:39.220 --> 00:28:40.650
Hi, Min-gi.

00:28:40.690 --> 00:28:42.850
Someone came to see you
early this morning.

00:28:42.890 --> 00:28:43.820
Who was it?

00:28:43.860 --> 00:28:46.090
Oh Moosung. Do you know him?
He's one mean-looking guy.

00:28:46.130 --> 00:28:48.020
Moosung? I don't know him.

00:28:48.070 --> 00:28:49.530
Anything else?

00:28:49.570 --> 00:28:51.960
Moon Suk is looking for you.
You want to talk to him now?

00:28:52.000 --> 00:28:54.940
No, Min-gi, don't put him through.

00:28:55.840 --> 00:28:57.670
I'll be going to the hotel soon.

00:29:05.920 --> 00:29:07.780
Well, well, well.

00:29:09.180 --> 00:29:10.180
Bottoms up.

00:29:10.220 --> 00:29:11.810
Someone's coming.

00:29:11.860 --> 00:29:14.450
Hey, Sunwoo, come over here.

00:29:14.490 --> 00:29:15.750
Sunwoo?

00:29:17.090 --> 00:29:18.120
Hello.

00:29:18.160 --> 00:29:19.190
Come here, come.

00:29:19.230 --> 00:29:20.090
Come.

00:29:20.130 --> 00:29:22.060
Why don't you come over
here for a second?

00:29:22.100 --> 00:29:24.760
Ji-hyun, this is Mr. Kim's seat.

00:29:24.800 --> 00:29:26.330
Come.

00:29:28.840 --> 00:29:30.260
Have a seat.

00:29:30.310 --> 00:29:33.730
Hey, why are you always so
secretive about the thing you do?

00:29:33.780 --> 00:29:35.360
What's up?

00:29:35.400 --> 00:29:36.400
Have a drink.

00:29:36.450 --> 00:29:38.570
Girls, get out.

00:29:38.610 --> 00:29:39.640
What are you doing?

00:29:39.680 --> 00:29:42.040
Don't ruin the fun. Relax.

00:29:42.080 --> 00:29:44.180
Say hello to President Baek.

00:29:44.220 --> 00:29:46.480
From the Baek-Sang Management Agency.

00:29:49.490 --> 00:29:51.480
Hi. I'm sorry I was rude
the other day.

00:29:51.530 --> 00:29:54.320
- I guess we had a misunderstanding.
- Is that why you came here?

00:29:54.360 --> 00:29:55.660
Yes, that and...

00:29:55.700 --> 00:29:58.860
There was no misunderstanding.

00:29:58.900 --> 00:30:00.890
Who do you think we are?

00:30:01.940 --> 00:30:04.000
- Hey, Sunwoo!
- You be quiet.

00:30:04.640 --> 00:30:06.570
Don't use your people
to mess with me anymore.

00:30:06.610 --> 00:30:07.630
Sunwoo!

00:30:08.680 --> 00:30:11.170
He's here as my guest today!

00:30:12.580 --> 00:30:16.640
Damn it, how could you
do this to me?

00:30:16.680 --> 00:30:18.310
I can do this because it's you.

00:30:26.360 --> 00:30:31.490
Kim Sunwoo, do you think
the world is all yours?

00:30:33.430 --> 00:30:35.090
Don't do anything you'll regret.

00:31:00.120 --> 00:31:01.120
Aren't you going?

00:31:01.160 --> 00:31:03.290
- You go first.
- See you.

00:31:53.710 --> 00:31:54.840
Heesoo.

00:31:56.080 --> 00:31:57.410
Hi.

00:31:59.180 --> 00:32:00.670
Did you have a good date today?

00:32:00.720 --> 00:32:02.180
Stop kidding.

00:32:04.790 --> 00:32:06.650
Where did you say
you'd sleep tonight?

00:32:12.760 --> 00:32:13.760
Thanks.

00:32:14.450 --> 00:32:15.450
How should we do this?

00:32:15.500 --> 00:32:17.290
I will call you tomorrow.

00:32:19.900 --> 00:32:20.990
Just call me...

00:33:20.530 --> 00:33:21.790
Yeah, Min-gi.

00:33:26.560 --> 00:33:29.360
That asshole can't drive for shit!

00:33:29.400 --> 00:33:30.960
I wasn't talking...

00:33:33.140 --> 00:33:34.610
I wasn't talking to you.

00:33:35.410 --> 00:33:36.600
What about Moon Suk?

00:33:37.610 --> 00:33:39.370
Did you go down to the club?

00:33:40.310 --> 00:33:41.570
Ok.

00:34:38.370 --> 00:34:39.370
Who is it?

00:34:44.210 --> 00:34:45.670
Who is it?

00:35:13.500 --> 00:35:14.560
Seyoon, don't!

00:35:19.070 --> 00:35:20.430
Seyoon!

00:35:20.470 --> 00:35:21.530
Stop it!

00:35:27.080 --> 00:35:28.080
You bastard!

00:36:12.420 --> 00:36:14.550
You know who I'm calling, don't you?

00:36:17.200 --> 00:36:19.030
Any last words?

00:36:42.280 --> 00:36:44.010
You finish them off yourself.

00:37:37.300 --> 00:37:38.930
Okay. This is what we'll do.

