01:22:51.210 --> 01:22:52.210
See?

01:22:52.810 --> 01:22:54.440
Fast, fast, fast.

01:22:55.520 --> 01:22:57.240
Take a good look.

01:22:57.280 --> 01:22:58.440
Now, first...

01:22:58.490 --> 01:23:00.810
unscrew this...

01:23:00.850 --> 01:23:04.520
then push this up and in.

01:23:04.560 --> 01:23:06.080
Easy, huh? Next...

01:23:06.130 --> 01:23:08.120
load the magazine...

01:23:08.160 --> 01:23:09.750
And then... bang.

01:23:12.970 --> 01:23:14.330
Simple, isn't it?

01:23:14.370 --> 01:23:16.890
Try one more time. Here.

01:23:25.750 --> 01:23:28.210
Okay, let's see how well
you were watching.

01:23:28.250 --> 01:23:29.370
They said they'll call back right away.

01:23:29.420 --> 01:23:30.580
Alright, alright, one second.

01:23:30.620 --> 01:23:32.010
Hey, look at this.

01:23:32.050 --> 01:23:35.950
Let's start at the same time,
okay?

01:23:35.990 --> 01:23:39.080
Hey, no bullets. Ready?

01:23:39.120 --> 01:23:41.060
One, two, three.

01:23:55.670 --> 01:23:58.160
Damn.

01:24:00.280 --> 01:24:02.870
Hello? Who?

01:24:02.910 --> 01:24:04.440
Ah, Mr. Han.

01:24:06.850 --> 01:24:09.240
You sent me someone?

01:24:09.290 --> 01:24:12.590
You know, the errand guy.

01:24:14.090 --> 01:24:15.250
Huh?

01:25:07.010 --> 01:25:09.840
What's with him? Drunk again?

01:26:13.600 --> 01:26:15.260
Brother!

01:26:15.310 --> 01:26:17.800
Why aren't you answering?

01:26:17.840 --> 01:26:19.240
You not around?

01:26:19.280 --> 01:26:21.100
I just arrived.

01:26:21.150 --> 01:26:22.810
I'm bringing the merchandise.

01:26:22.850 --> 01:26:25.010
I'll be there in about an hour.

01:26:25.050 --> 01:26:26.210
See you then.

01:27:03.790 --> 01:27:06.780
Stop staring at me
and call President Baek.

01:27:10.290 --> 01:27:11.990
I don't have much time.

01:28:35.740 --> 01:28:38.210
What are you doing?
Hurry up man...

01:28:39.580 --> 01:28:42.240
The ice rink, right?

01:28:43.620 --> 01:28:46.170
I've been waiting here forever.

01:28:48.650 --> 01:28:50.880
Call me right away when you get
this message.

01:28:57.390 --> 01:28:59.760
Damn, it's fucking cold in here.

01:29:31.660 --> 01:29:33.390
Surprised?

01:29:33.430 --> 01:29:38.330
Thought you'd never
see me again? Smile.

01:29:41.370 --> 01:29:44.360
Hey, let's be professional.

01:29:44.410 --> 01:29:49.970
I thought about it, and lots of
people have bad memories, right?

01:29:50.010 --> 01:29:53.040
Memories that can never
be erased, no matter what.

01:29:54.250 --> 01:29:57.180
But at least you can erase
the traces...

01:29:57.220 --> 01:29:59.650
I mean, the people who caused
those memories.

01:29:59.690 --> 01:30:01.650
What are you talking about?

01:30:01.690 --> 01:30:05.620
Life is full of all kinds of shit.
Why are you acting like a child?

01:30:05.660 --> 01:30:08.650
I'm saying that you're just
a shitty memory for me.

01:30:08.700 --> 01:30:09.700
And I'm...

01:30:14.400 --> 01:30:16.530
oh, never mind.
Let me ask you one thing.

01:30:17.700 --> 01:30:19.600
Why did you do that to me?

01:30:25.180 --> 01:30:28.170
Oh for fuck's sake...

01:30:35.320 --> 01:30:36.880
Hey, Mr. Sunwoo...

01:30:39.060 --> 01:30:40.960
You bastard.

01:30:42.730 --> 01:30:44.790
Damn, you piece of shit!

01:30:46.700 --> 01:30:49.000
You fucking asshole!

01:30:49.700 --> 01:30:52.360
You thought I was an amateur?

01:30:57.910 --> 01:31:00.540
What's that supposed to mean?

01:31:01.080 --> 01:31:04.850
You think it's unfair? Unfair?

01:31:06.180 --> 01:31:08.380
Can't you figure out
the reason for all this?

01:31:08.420 --> 01:31:10.950
You keep looking
in all the wrong places.

01:31:10.990 --> 01:31:13.920
Then you shouldn't have come to me.

01:31:17.300 --> 01:31:19.250
Life is about suffering.

01:31:19.300 --> 01:31:20.590
Didn't you know that?

01:31:20.630 --> 01:31:22.820
Hey you, stand up straight.
Straight.

01:31:22.870 --> 01:31:26.230
I'll teach you a lesson.
Stand up straight.

01:31:30.140 --> 01:31:31.840
Just a moment. Wait.

01:32:01.640 --> 01:32:03.100
Damn.

01:32:07.740 --> 01:32:09.140
Ah, fuck.

01:32:16.820 --> 01:32:18.680
What was that?

01:32:20.690 --> 01:32:22.380
Oh, hi, how are you?

01:32:23.930 --> 01:32:26.950
Did you hear some kind of bang?

01:32:27.760 --> 01:32:29.960
The sound of a hole
being ripped out of life.

01:32:30.000 --> 01:32:33.030
Huh? Oh, okay.

01:32:33.070 --> 01:32:36.500
Things are tough these days.
Everyone's having hard times.

01:32:36.540 --> 01:32:38.600
It's getting cold.
Winter's coming.

01:32:38.640 --> 01:32:39.830
It's too damn hard to live.

01:32:39.870 --> 01:32:42.770
I wonder what the politicians
are doing for us.

01:32:42.810 --> 01:32:48.110
Because of the new bus-only lanes,
Driving downtown is harder.

01:32:48.150 --> 01:32:51.140
Mister, please take me downtown.

01:32:51.180 --> 01:32:52.480
Oh, okay.

01:33:03.260 --> 01:33:08.460
You messed with the wrong guy.
Watch yourself.

01:33:22.610 --> 01:33:23.610
Damn.

01:33:25.550 --> 01:33:26.710
Untie the ropes.

01:33:36.620 --> 01:33:37.620
Bring me a phone.

01:33:37.660 --> 01:33:38.350
What?

01:33:38.400 --> 01:33:40.590
Bring me a phone, you asshole!

01:34:06.660 --> 01:34:08.890
I'll make it short.

01:34:11.360 --> 01:34:13.260
You've seen Sunwoo, right?

01:34:16.130 --> 01:34:17.860
You mean Mr. Kim?

01:34:18.370 --> 01:34:19.560
That's right, Manager Kim.

01:34:19.600 --> 01:34:22.200
You haven't seen him lately,
have you? Where is he?

01:34:23.240 --> 01:34:25.430
How would I know?

01:34:50.700 --> 01:34:54.360
Hey Mi-ae. I'm on my way now.

01:34:56.000 --> 01:34:57.000
Yes.

01:35:02.480 --> 01:35:05.270
[1 Missed Call: KIM Sunwoo]

01:35:17.460 --> 01:35:20.650
Get out. Hurry up!

01:35:20.690 --> 01:35:22.360
Hey! Hurry up!

01:36:01.570 --> 01:36:04.870
I'll be downstairs.
So call me if something happens.

01:36:18.020 --> 01:36:23.450
Here. That guy dropped this off
and just left.

01:37:38.460 --> 01:37:40.150
How did it get to this point?

01:37:46.730 --> 01:37:48.260
It's okay.

01:37:50.140 --> 01:37:52.040
It's okay...

01:38:12.420 --> 01:38:14.190
Moon Suk.

01:38:15.690 --> 01:38:17.180
Who's that?

01:39:52.220 --> 01:39:54.120
You can't come this way, sir.

01:41:32.520 --> 01:41:34.880
Let's not make a fuss.

01:41:36.550 --> 01:41:38.250
This is my last stop.

01:41:39.790 --> 01:41:41.650
I've nowhere to go.

01:41:56.770 --> 01:42:00.610
You really want to take it this far?

01:42:02.240 --> 01:42:04.300
Why did you do that to me?

01:42:07.180 --> 01:42:10.580
Tell me why.

01:42:12.150 --> 01:42:14.920
You insulted me.

01:42:15.490 --> 01:42:19.450
No, not that kind of thing.
Tell me the real reason.

01:42:25.160 --> 01:42:26.720
Tell me.

01:42:28.640 --> 01:42:35.100
I've been thinking about this
a lot, and I still don't get it.

01:42:37.910 --> 01:42:43.540
Tell me, how did we come to this?

01:42:45.950 --> 01:42:48.040
How did this happen?

01:42:48.090 --> 01:42:50.950
Were you really going to kill me?

01:42:52.920 --> 01:42:56.120
Were you really?

01:42:56.160 --> 01:43:01.690
I've served you like a dog,
for 7 years.

01:43:02.600 --> 01:43:04.260
Say me something.

01:43:05.200 --> 01:43:07.690
Anything. Tell me!

01:43:49.680 --> 01:43:54.210
What's gotten into you?

01:43:57.390 --> 01:43:59.150
Was it because of her?

01:44:17.310 --> 01:44:18.830
Don't do this.

01:45:10.020 --> 01:45:13.650
But we can't turn back
time now, can we?

01:51:20.240 --> 01:51:21.730
Hello?

01:51:27.680 --> 01:51:30.550
Hello?

01:52:10.360 --> 01:52:12.450
This is too harsh...

01:54:35.730 --> 01:54:41.590
One late autumn night,
the disciple woke up crying.

01:54:41.630 --> 01:54:46.870
So the master asked the disciple...

01:54:47.740 --> 01:54:52.040
- "Did you have a nightmare?"
- "No."

01:54:52.080 --> 01:54:54.570
"Did you have a sad dream?"

01:54:54.610 --> 01:54:56.910
"No," said the disciple.

01:54:56.950 --> 01:54:59.470
"I had a sweet dream."

01:55:00.390 --> 01:55:03.450
Then why are you crying so sadly?

01:55:03.490 --> 01:55:08.860
The disciple answered quietly,
while wiping his tears...

01:55:09.930 --> 01:55:14.520
"Because the dream
I had can't come true."
